WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.720
Hello, my name is Li Feng.

00:04.720 --> 00:09.120
I'm your teacher and you're my students.

00:09.120 --> 00:11.200
I'm Chinese.

00:11.200 --> 00:13.840
I'm from Wuhan.

00:13.840 --> 00:15.760
What's your name?

00:15.760 --> 00:18.880
My name is Wang Ling Ling.

00:18.880 --> 00:21.680
Nice to meet you, Ling Ling.

00:21.680 --> 00:23.520
Where are you from?

00:23.520 --> 00:25.520
I'm from Beijing.

00:25.520 --> 00:27.520
I'm Chinese.

00:27.520 --> 00:29.120
How old are you?

00:29.200 --> 00:31.600
I'm 13 years old.

00:31.600 --> 00:33.360
Good.

00:33.360 --> 00:36.880
Hello, what about you?

00:36.880 --> 00:39.040
Hello, Miss Li.

00:39.040 --> 00:44.160
My name is Li Daming and I'm from Beijing too.

00:44.160 --> 00:47.120
I'm 12 years old.

00:47.120 --> 00:49.200
Thanks.

00:49.200 --> 00:53.040
Hello, are you from America?

00:53.040 --> 00:55.360
No, I'm not.

00:55.360 --> 00:57.440
I'm from England.

00:57.440 --> 00:59.680
I'm Tony Smith.

00:59.680 --> 01:02.640
Nice to meet you, Tony.

01:02.640 --> 01:03.840
Hi.

01:03.840 --> 01:06.400
Are you English too?

01:06.400 --> 01:08.720
No, I'm not.

01:08.720 --> 01:13.680
I'm American and my name is Betty King.

01:13.680 --> 01:16.880
Tony and Betty are our friends.

01:16.880 --> 01:18.400
Good.

01:18.400 --> 01:22.080
Welcome to Class 4, Grade 7.

